mixin types
    .font.font_size_h1
      .font__tag H1
      .font__task This one is the sub-section or widget title
    .font.font_size_h2
      .font__tag H2
      .font__task Next one is the item title inside widgets
    .font.font_size_h3
      .font__tag H3
      .font__task This is a label or CTA text
    .font.font_size_body
      .font__tag Body
      .font__task This is the body text which is used for most of the design, like paragraphs, lists, etc.